Class ExecutedExamsController

  • java.lang.Object

    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class ExecutedExamsController
extends Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    This class is used as controller for Executed Exams screen. The screen show the exectued exams by the student and his grades if the grade approved All the details are inserted into the table and showed to the client
